rows.label: bf11380150_0010
rows.name: Sata, can you chop the veggies?

rows.label: bf11380150_0040
rows.name: Not really. Anyone could do it.

rows.label: bf11380150_0050
rows.name:
Looks like there's nothing to worry about here.
Well then, I'll take care of the meat...

rows.label: bf11380150_0080
rows.name: What do you think you're doing?

rows.label: bf11380150_0090
rows.name: What does it look like? I'm preparing the meat.

rows.label: bf11380150_0100
rows.name:
Stop, get away from there!
Please, just don't touch anything!

rows.label: bf11380150_0140
rows.name:
You have no idea what you're talking about. You don't
understand the destructive force of Hikari's cooking.

rows.label: bf11380150_0160
rows.name: A [System:Ruby rt=Device ]Servants[/System:Ruby] is nothing compared to Hikari's cooking!

rows.label: bf11380150_0170
rows.name:
Hey, watch it!
Don't go around saying mean things like that.

rows.label: bf11380150_0200
rows.name: Could you come here for a minute?

rows.label: bf11380150_0210
rows.name:
What?
I'm about to make dinner[ML:Dash]

rows.label: bf11380150_0220
rows.name: Laura, you too. Could you both spar with me for a bit?

rows.label: bf11380150_0250
rows.name: Really? Then, I'll leave it to you.

rows.label: bf11380150_0280
rows.name: Want to... try some next time?
